snippet.textDisplay:
The music in this is like at the start the song has a melody, but a few seconds later it changes to an erratic tune, like a short circuit in a computer. The rest of the song involves it trying to find the melody and seems to find it at the violin portions but after the wind-down, the short-circuiting continues.

Hence the track's title
